  {id:'ghidorah',name:'King Ghidorah',alias:'Monster Zero / The One Who Is Many',emoji:'🐉',id_code:'T-002',alignment:'hostile',status:'deceased',threat:'Omega',height:'158m',weight:'141,056 tons',habitat:'Deep Space / Ice Shelf (Antarctica)',first:'1964',era:'MonsterVerse',powers:['Gravity Beams','EMP','Storm Generation','Rapid Regeneration','Psychic Control'],weaknesses:['Nuclear Supercharge','Godzilla Alpha Call'],appearances:['King of the Monsters','GvK (Mechagodzilla)'],bio:'An extraterrestrial parasite that arrived on Earth thousands of years ago. Ghidorah does not follow the natural alpha hierarchy — he overrides it, broadcasting psychic control signals that subvert Titan biology. Unlike native Titans, he does not restore balance; he drives ecosystems to collapse. Decapitated head recovered by Apex Cybernetics post-KotM.',power:92},
