  {id:'kong',name:'Kong',alias:'The Last Skar King / Lord of the Hollow Earth',emoji:'🦍',id_code:'T-004',alignment:'alpha',status:'alive',threat:'High',height:'102m',weight:'50,000 tons',habitat:'Skull Island / Hollow Earth',first:'1933',era:'MonsterVerse',powers:['Primate Intelligence','Battle Axe (HEAV)','Combat Agility','Hollow Earth Navigation','Skar King Chain'],weaknesses:['Physical endurance limits','Water (early)'],appearances:['Skull Island','GvK','GxK'],bio:'Last of the Iwi-bonded Kongs, inheritor of the Hollow Earth throne. Kong\'s intelligence distinguishes him from standard Titans — he uses tools, forms alliances, and understands tactical positioning. His relationship with humanity began with the Iwi tribe on Skull Island. His B.E.A.V. battle axe is forged from Godzilla dorsal plate material.',power:86},
  {id:'rodan',name:'Rodan',alias:'The Fire Demon',emoji:'🦅',id_code:'T-005',alignment:'neutral',status:'dormant',threat:'High',height:'154m wingspan',weight:'30,000 tons',habitat:'Isla de Mara, Mexico / Volcanic chambers',first:'1956',era:'MonsterVerse',powers:['Mach 3 Flight','Thermonuclear Heat Absorption','Shockwave Wings','Molten Rock Armor'],weaknesses:['Alpha dominance override','Sustained combat'],appearances:['King of the Monsters'],bio:'A volcanic Titan who sustained himself in dormancy inside the magma chamber of Isla de Mara. Rodan is opportunistic — he submitted to Ghidorah\'s psychic alpha call, then switched allegiance to Godzilla after the latter\'s nuclear supercharge. Classified as neutral alignment due to demonstrated opportunism.',power:74},
  {id:'mechagodzilla',name:'Mechagodzilla',alias:'Apex Unit / Controlled Ghidorah',emoji:'🤖',id_code:'T-006',alignment:'hostile',status:'deceased',threat:'Omega',height:'118m',weight:'100,000 tons',habitat:'Apex Cybernetics Facility, Pensacola',first:'1974',era:'MonsterVerse',powers:['Proton Scream','Razor Wings','Tail Drill','Telekinetic Override','Neural Uplink (Ghidorah)'],weaknesses:['Hollow Earth power source disruption','Godzilla Nuclear Pulse'],appearances:['Godzilla vs. Kong'],bio:'Apex Cybernetics\' mechanical Titan built using King Ghidorah\'s severed skull as a neural relay. The skull retained Ghidorah\'s consciousness — upon activation, Ghidorah\'s mind overrode Apex\'s control systems and the mech went rogue. Destroyed by Godzilla and Kong in combined assault. All remains impounded by Monarch.',power:90},
  {id:'shimo',name:'Shimo',alias:'The Primordial / Skar King\'s Prisoner',emoji:'🧊',id_code:'T-007',alignment:'benevolent',status:'alive',threat:'Omega',height:'135m',weight:'87,000 tons',habitat:'Hollow Earth Glacial Zone',first:'Ancient era',era:'MonsterVerse',powers:['Absolute Zero Freeze Ray','Blizzard Breath','Ice Crystal Generation','Cryogenic Field','Ancient Titan Strength'],weaknesses:['Domination Crystal (Skar King)','Extreme heat'],appearances:['Godzilla x Kong: The New Empire'],bio:'One of the most powerful Titans ever classified — an ancient ice-elemental Titan enslaved by the Skar King using a Domination Crystal. Freed by Kong during the Hollow Earth conflict. Shimo\'s freeze ray can encircle the planet in glacial winter if sustained — a living extinction event. Post-liberation, she has shown no aggression toward humanity.',power:93},
